### health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/

### register
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo_user",
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "12345678"
}

### login
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo_user",
  "password": "12345678"
}

### profile
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer demo-access-token:demo_user

### change password
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer demo-access-token:demo_user

{
  "username": "demo_user",
  "old_password": "12345678",
  "new_password": "87654321",
  "confirm_password": "87654321"
}

### list documents
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/vector-store/documents

### chat
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/chat/completion
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "请介绍一下这个项目",
  "collection_name": "default",
  "top_k": 3,
  "history": []
}

### profile (use token from register/login response)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### change password (use token from register/login response)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

{
  "username": "demo_user",
  "old_password": "12345678",
  "new_password": "87654321",
  "confirm_password": "87654321"
}
